<p style="text-align: center;"><tt><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notexam-houses" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4301802); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4301802&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610201885" alt="Notexam Houses" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4301802)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/notexam-houses" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4301802); return false;">Notexam Houses</a></span></strong></tt></p>
