<div class="preview {$background}">
<p><strong><a href="/scp-cn-541">SCP-CN-541</a></strong><br />
+<strong><tt>15</tt></strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;</span><sup>&#8230;</sup> <strong><tt>10</tt></strong><br />
<em>最新评论：</em> <strong><tt>Rachud</tt></strong> <em>于</em> <strong><tt><span class="odate time_1561107758 format_%25D%20%25H%3A%25M">21 Jun 2019 09:02</span></tt></strong><br />
